<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 02:12:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队袭击加沙地带并打捞失踪以色列人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-gaza-strip-retrieves-bodies-of-missing-israelis/0000018b-2bc6-dff1-a5eb-ffff1b670000</link><description>以色列证实地面部队已进入加沙地带，“摧毁了恐怖分子小队和基础设施”，并发现了可能导致更多人员失踪的物品</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-gaza-strip-retrieves-bodies-of-missing-israelis/0000018b-2bc6-dff1-a5eb-ffff1b670000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击后对以色列南部的一次令人毛骨悚然的访问唤起了伊斯兰国和乌克兰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-bloodcurdling-visit-to-israels-south-after-the-hamas-attack-evokes-isis-and-ukraine/0000018b-2b0a-d1bc-a58b-6bafb8550000</link><description>本周，斯德洛特和附近其他城镇的街道空无一人，但仍能看到烧毁的汽车和血迹，枪战的声音清晰可闻。以色列从未发生过这样的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-bloodcurdling-visit-to-israels-south-after-the-hamas-attack-evokes-isis-and-ukraine/0000018b-2b0a-d1bc-a58b-6bafb8550000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯的袭击是内部人员所为”：为什么疯狂的阴谋论如此流行？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-attack-was-an-inside-job-why-are-wild-conspiracy-theories-so-popular/0000018b-2a03-dff1-a5eb-fefff50d0000</link><description>一些以色列右翼人士将加沙战争归咎于以色列国防军高层或反政府抗议者。从比比主义者到特朗普，研究为寻找“内部叛徒”提供了一些线索</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 21:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-attack-was-an-inside-job-why-are-wild-conspiracy-theories-so-popular/0000018b-2a03-dff1-a5eb-fefff50d0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部称，两名巴勒斯坦人在定居者袭击救护车中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-settler-attack-on-ambulances-palestinian-health-ministry-says/0000018b-2550-d680-af9b-27dec5a90000</link><description>以色列军队参加了部分预先安排的袭击，目前尚不清楚是谁射杀了两名巴勒斯坦人——一对父子——。袭击的救护车载着在附近村庄被杀的巴勒斯坦人的尸体，该地区有武装定居者的记录</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 21:41:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-14/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-settler-attack-on-ambulances-palestinian-health-ministry-says/0000018b-2550-d680-af9b-27dec5a90000</guid></item><item><title>“完全是假的”：以色列国家安全顾问否认收到埃及关于哈马斯袭击的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-adviser-denies-receiving-egyptian-warning-of-hamas-attack/0000018b-28c9-d1bc-a58b-69ef2ed70000</link><description>国家安全顾问查奇·哈内格比表示，在美国议员告诉记者“埃及三天前已警告以色列人”后，以色列收到了有关哈马斯袭击的“零信息”</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 19:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-security-adviser-denies-receiving-egyptian-warning-of-hamas-attack/0000018b-28c9-d1bc-a58b-69ef2ed70000</guid></item><item><title>“这关乎犹太人的存在”：以色列与哈马斯的战争蔓延到哥伦比亚大学校园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/this-is-about-jewish-existence-israel-hamas-war-spills-into-columbia-campus/0000018b-29f2-dff1-a5eb-ffffdfec0000</link><description>校园里有越战以来最大规模的警察，亲巴勒斯坦的学生聚集在哥伦比亚大学，当一名发言者将以色列公民的屠杀描述为“对定居者殖民压迫者的反击”时，他们欢呼雀跃。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 17:55:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/this-is-about-jewish-existence-israel-hamas-war-spills-into-columbia-campus/0000018b-29f2-dff1-a5eb-ffffdfec0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：由于与哈马斯的持续战争，沙特阿拉伯冻结了与以色列的正常化谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-freezes-normalization-talks-with-israel-amid-ongoing-war-with-hamas/0000018b-2a0b-d1bc-a58b-6baf83c20000</link><description>这场冲突还促使沙特与伊朗接触。沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼接到伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西打来的第一个电话，利雅得试图阻止该地区更广泛的暴力事件激增</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 17:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-freezes-normalization-talks-with-israel-amid-ongoing-war-with-hamas/0000018b-2a0b-d1bc-a58b-6baf83c20000</guid></item><item><title>进步人士警告以色列在加沙进行“种族清洗”，与主流民主党的分歧扩大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/progressives-warn-of-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza-widening-rift-with-mainstream-dems/0000018b-29b4-dff1-a5eb-fffdfc710000</link><description>这些言论发表之际，进步人士与其同事之间的分歧日益扩大，他们谴责他们最初的回应不够充分，并提供了虚假的对等内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 15:58:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/progressives-warn-of-ethnic-cleansing-in-gaza-widening-rift-with-mainstream-dems/0000018b-29b4-dff1-a5eb-fffdfc710000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯告诉阿巴斯，约旦国王阿卜杜拉：哈马斯不代表巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/blinken-tells-abbas-jordans-king-abdullah-hamas-doesnt-stand-for-palestinians/0000018b-2950-d628-a3af-fdd9de9e0000</link><description>在与阿卜杜拉会面期间，他们讨论了确保人质获释的努力、防止冲突扩大的重要性以及加沙平民的人道主义需求</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 14:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/blinken-tells-abbas-jordans-king-abdullah-hamas-doesnt-stand-for-palestinians/0000018b-2950-d628-a3af-fdd9de9e0000</guid></item><item><title>不方便的背景：巴勒斯坦人因为犹太人而屠杀犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</link><description>坚持认为加沙周边以色列社区 1,300 多人被谋杀只是有政治背景，就是故意忽视哈马斯、真主党、法国和巴基斯坦伊斯兰主义者谋杀犹太人与匹兹堡枪击案之间的联系</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 13:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-inconvenient-context-palestinians-massacred-jews-for-being-jews/0000018b-2890-dff1-a5eb-fefd6e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>布鲁克林篮网队与拉阿纳纳马卡比队的 NBA 季前赛变成了对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</link><description>在哈马斯周六对以色列平民进行屠杀之后，与以色列有关的一切都不再一样了——包括周四以色列球队与美国 NBA 对手之间的例行篮球比赛</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/brooklyn-nets-maccabi-raanana-pre-season-game-turns-into-show-of-support-for-israel/0000018b-2889-d450-a3af-699d1ed60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者记录在西岸近距离射杀巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-documented-shooting-palestinian-at-point-blank-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-28e3-d450-a3af-69ffcb950000</link><description>该事件发生在希伯伦以南的巴勒斯坦阿图瓦尼村附近。镜头中还可以看到一名以色列国防军士兵站在定居者附近的背景中</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:23:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-documented-shooting-palestinian-at-point-blank-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-28e3-d450-a3af-69ffcb950000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的品牌：没有责任，没有责任，没有悔恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</link><description>周四，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡组建了“临时战时内阁”，将他的零责任、始终分担责任的态度提升到了一个新的水平。在任何其他情况下，这都是正确的做法——对他来说，这只是确保加沙战争失败的责任归咎于其他人的另一种方式</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-on-brand-no-responsibility-no-accountability-no-remorse/0000018b-288d-d450-a3af-699d263a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质是以色列的致命弱点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</link><description>被哈马斯在加沙绑架的以色列人（其中包括妇女、儿童、婴儿和老人）的视频和图像令人痛苦，触动了以色列政体最柔软、最脆弱的弱点</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hostages-are-israels-achilles-heel/0000018b-2622-d3fc-a3bf-bfef934e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新的哈马斯-加沙概念注定会失败，就像上一个概念一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</link><description>以色列对待哈马斯的态度是错误的，将其视为一个政治组织，可以通过经济激励来影响其取得成果。像对待伊斯兰国一样对哈马斯发动战争是一个谬论，它掩盖了加沙地带冲突后控制问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-concept-of-hamas-and-gaza-is-doomed-to-fail-just-like-the-last-one/0000018b-27bb-d1bc-a58b-6fbf9edf0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国和欧洲的支持下，以色列正在摧毁加沙。它必须考虑后天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</link><description>哈马斯的恐怖袭击和以色列受害者的数量令人难以想象。与此同时，加沙人面临的只有地狱和毁灭。一旦复仇的欲望稍稍消退，我们必须要问：加沙将会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-and-european-support-israel-is-crushing-gaza-it-must-think-about-the-day-after/0000018b-2802-dff1-a5eb-feff0c720000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带的起源及其周围的以色列社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</link><description>加沙汹涌的仇恨之海正是这些以色列社区本应“笼罩”的</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-origins-of-the-gaza-strip-and-the-israeli-communities-nestled-by-it/0000018b-23fe-d680-af9b-23fe94490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军监测以色列-加沙边境的气球在哈马斯袭击前几周破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</link><description>以色列军队上周未能修复边境监控技术；目前正在研究哈马斯破坏气球的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-balloons-monitoring-israel-gaza-border-broke-down-weeks-before-hamas-attack/0000018b-2831-d1bc-a58b-69b7dd400000</guid></item><item><title>研究揭示了中东史前暴力的范围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</link><description>对 14,000 至 2,400 年前的 3,500 具骨骼的分析发现了暴力历史中的细微差别。有时可以包容</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-13/ty-article/study-reveals-the-scope-of-prehistoric-violence-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-2416-d3fc-a3bf-bfffeddc0000</guid></item><item><title>这就是乌克兰与以色列站在一起的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</link><description>针对以色列的可怕恐怖袭击引起了乌克兰人的共鸣。火箭、酷刑和谋杀、绑架儿童——我们太了解这个剧本了。但我们的悲剧的相似之处并非偶然</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:02:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/this-is-why-ukraine-stands-with-israel/0000018b-2629-d680-af9b-26ef410a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>